dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misaha al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Al Budayr section.] Alternate title: Liwa' ad-Diwaniyah: qada' 'Afak: nahiyat Al Budayr. [ad-Diwaniyah province: Afak district: Al Budayr section.] Relief shown by hachures, form lines, and countor intervals at .5 meter intervals. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed 1931. Tribal lands and land ownership are shown.
